-- Gold Futures Gain, Extending Weekly Advance on Speculation Demand to Rise
-- Wendy Pugh
-- 2010-07-11T22:07:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-11/gold-futures-gain-extending-weekly-advance-on-speculation-demand-to-rise.html

          
          
             Gold for August delivery in New York
gained 0.2 percent to $1,211.90 an ounce at 8:01 a.m. Melbourne
time after advancing by 0.2 percent last week.  
